SeqItems.ItemName: Switch Fixture CC pin to CC1

SeqItems.ExpectStr: Hit any key to stop autoboot:

SeqItems.ComdOrParam: setenv machid 8060080 && usb start && imgaddr=0x44000000 &&  fatload usb 0:1 $imgaddr emmc-ipq5332-single-<ImageVer>.img && source $imgaddr:script
dd if=/dev/zero of=/dev/mmcblk0p24 bs=10M count=1 conv=fsync
dd if=/dev/zero of=/dev/mmcblk0p25 bs=10M count=1 conv=fsync
ifconfig br-lan down && brctl delbr br-lan

SeqItems.ItemName: Switch Fixture CC pin to CC2 from CC1
